WHO   — The Handmaids — the conscripted wombs
WHAT  — The institution at the book's heart: women reduced to ‘two-legged wombs,’ renamed for their masters, reassigned when they fail.
WHERE — HMT · THE HANDMAID'S TALE  Framework inputs: The Handmaid's Tale (Margaret Atwood, 1985)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
